The mushrooms were gone in about five minutes. Excellent recipe. I had a little extra filling, so I used it as a dip for tortilla chips. It is very rich and a little greasy. Perfect for parties. I will make this again at my next party!

Rating: 4
What a great recipe. I substituted sweet sausage for the hot and the results were terrific. Very rich but great combination. Easy to make ahead and just pop in the oven when guests arrive. Many commented they were the best stuffed mushrooms they had ever eaten. A keeper!

Rating: 4
Fabulous! Not your usual greasy sausage stuffed mushrooms. I have always done crab stuffed mushrooms instead to try to keep things more elegant. Threw these on the menu for a cocktail party at the last minute because they were so easy and could be made ahead. Everyone loved them - especially the men. Even a friend who is a gourmet chef kept going back for more and asked for the recipe! These will be a menu staple from now on.

