Rating: 4
Made this recipe for three different Christmas parties - all to raving reviews. (My ONLY change was to sub a tube of Jimmy Dean's regular sausage and a tube of the JD's Hot sausage - for a double recipe). The first time I made these was for my wife's staff party for 14 people. My wife came into the kitchen, collapsed against the counter and procaimed, "Those stuffed mushrooms, oh my gosh, they're fantastic!" Not too much later a guest rushed in yelling, "Those mushrooms ROCK!" My brother-in-law at Christmas hates stuffed mushrooms and devoured 4 of them. Needless to say, this recipe works.

